            <title>[SOLR-16889] Rate Limiter should stop processing on 429</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-16889</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Rate Limiter can issue a 429 in case of overload but it will not stop processing the request.&lt;br/&gt;
The client side will still get the correct response code.&lt;/p&gt;

